    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic deckbuilding cardbattler game with turn-based combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play one of three specializations and face the gangs of the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262640/extras/3820225c67243b1ff91fcc86f577f044.poster.avif?t=1732286496\" width=800 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262640/extras/3820225c67243b1ff91fcc86f577f044.webm?t=1732286496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262640/extras/3820225c67243b1ff91fcc86f577f044.mp4?t=1732286496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win fights, collect cards, build a strong deck and advance on the map. Level up your street rank by liberating oppressed communities. Loot and equip items to build your character and to improve your stats and chances on making it to the top.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262640/extras/64046eb03a75e79ad1a88ca68ee0e9e0.poster.avif?t=1732286496\" width=800 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262640/extras/64046eb03a75e79ad1a88ca68ee0e9e0.webm?t=1732286496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262640/extras/64046eb03a75e79ad1a88ca68ee0e9e0.mp4?t=1732286496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In your quest of finding your abducted dad who seems to be involved in the gang activities of the city, uncover who controls the gangs - and by that the whole city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your deck and your character and play your cards strategically to conquer the city before it conquers you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
